aracter is not a valid hex digit.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.hexDigitToUInt8?","kind":"def","line":107,"name":"Std.Http.URI.hexDigitToUInt8?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.lean#L107-L119"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.hexDigit\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">hexDigit</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">n</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt8\">UInt8</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt8\">UInt8</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Converts a nibble (4-bit value, 0-15) to its hexadecimal digit representation. Returns '0'-'9' for\nvalues 0-9, and 'A'-'F' for values 10-15.\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.hexDigit","kind":"def","line":99,"name":"Std.Http.URI.hexDigit","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.lean#L99-L105"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.isValidPercentEncoding\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">isValidPercentEncoding</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ba</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#ByteArray\">ByteArray</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Validates that all percent signs in a byte array are followed by exactly two hexadecimal digits.\nThis ensures proper percent-encoding according to RFC 3986.\n\nFor example:\n- `%20` is valid (percent followed by two hex digits)\n- `%` is invalid (percent with no following digits)\n- `%2` is invalid (percent followed by only one digit)\n- `%GG` is invalid (percent followed by non-hex characters)\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.isValidPercentEncoding","kind":"def","line":72,"name":"Std.Http.URI.isValidPercentEncoding","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.lean#L72-L97"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.instDecidableIsAllowedEncodedQueryChars\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">instDecidableIsAllowedEncodedQueryChars</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">r</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt8\">UInt8</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#ByteArray\">ByteArray</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Decidable\">Decidable</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.IsAllowedEncodedQueryChars\">IsAllowedEncodedQueryChars</a> <span class=\"fn\">r</span> <span class=\"fn\">s</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.instDecidableIsAllowedEncodedQueryChars","kind":"instance","line":69,"name":"Std.Http.URI.instDecidableIsAllowedEncodedQueryChars","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.lean#L69-L70"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.IsAllowedEncodedQueryChars\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">IsAllowedEncodedQueryChars</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">rule</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#UInt8\">UInt8</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#ByteArray\">ByteArray</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Prop</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Checks if all characters in a `ByteArray` are allowed in an encoded query parameter. Allows '+' as an\nalternative encoding for space (application/x-www-form-urlencoded).\n","docLink":"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.IsAllowedEncodedQueryChars","kind":"def","line":61,"name":"Std.Http.URI.IsAllowedEncodedQueryChars","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.lean#L61-L67"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Http/Data/URI/Encoding.html#Std.Http.URI.instDecidableIsAllowedEncodedChars\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Http</span>.<span class=\"name\">URI</span>.<span class=\"name\">instDecidableIsAllowedEncodedChars</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_a